  Stable on ppc.

  26 Apr 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.0-r1.ebuild,
  baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1.ebuild, baekmuk-fonts-2.1.ebuild:
