  07 Mar 2004; Bret Curtis <psi29a@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added ~mips to KEYWORDS

  09 Jan 2004; Jason Wever <weeve@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Marked stable on sparc.

*baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1 (31 Jul 2003)

  21 Aug 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Marked stable on x86 and alpha

  31 Jul 2003; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Changed default font path and font format from bdf to pcf.
  Added HOMEPAGE (in Korean). Added ~alpha keywords and two USE flags, 
  X and truetype. This closes bug #22401.

*baekmuk-fonts-2.1 (02 Jun 2003)

  03 Jul 2003; Guy Marin <gmsoft@gentoo.org> baekmuk-fonts-2.1.ebuild :
  Added hppa to KEYWORDS.

  02 Jun 2003; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org>
  baekmuk-fonts-2.0-r1.ebuild, baekmuk-fonts-2.1.ebuild:
  moved to media-fonts

